License: GPLv3


PURPOSE: reduces the amount of reads in a readfile at random
USAGE: python reduceReads.py inFile outFile ratio inputflag
Where infile is the read file
outfile is the new read file
ratio is the ratio of reads to include in the new read file (i.e. 0.5 reduces the number of reads by half)
and inputflag is the file format of the read file where the options are
fa - fasta file
fq - fastq file
faz - gzipped fasta file
fqz - gzipped fastq file
